PrayUp | Turn Worry Into Prayer

PrayUp is your personal prayer assistant — a peaceful space where you can submit your worries, fears, or intentions and instantly receive a custom-written prayer to uplift your spirit. Whether you're anxious, grateful, or seeking guidance, PrayUp transforms your thoughts into heartfelt prayers powered by AI and inspired by faith.

🕊️ How it works:

Type in what’s on your heart

Receive a prayer crafted just for you

Save, share, or reflect anytime

Built to comfort, encourage, and connect — one prayer at a time.
